---
layout: base.njk
title: Song Chords
description: Browse Malayalam Christian devotional songs with keyboard chords and tutorials. Learn Syro Malabar Holy Mass songs.
---

<style>
.songs-page-hero {
    background-color: var(--light-color);
    padding: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.search-bar {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 30px auto 0;
    position: relative;
}

.search-bar input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 15px 50px 15px 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: inherit;
}

.search-bar input:focus {
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.2);
}

.search-bar button {
    position: absolute;
    right: 5px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.search-bar button:hover {
    background: var(--dark-color);
}

.category-filters {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 30px 0;
}

.category-btn {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: var(--transition);
}

.category-btn:hover,
.category-btn.active {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
}

.songs-container {
    padding: 60px 0;
}

.songs-count {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
}

.songs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
}

.song-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 25px;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    transition: var(--transition);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.song-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
}

.song-card h3 {
    color: var(--dark-color);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.song-card p {
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
}

.song-details {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    margin: 15px 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
}

.song-details span {
    background: var(--light-color);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--dark-color);
}

.song-link {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: var(--transition);
}

.song-link:hover {
    background: var(--dark-color);
    color: white;
}

.load-more-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
}

.loading-indicator {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
}

.no-songs {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
}

.no-songs h3 {
    color: var(--dark-color);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}
</style>

<section class="songs-page-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Malayalam Christian Song Chords</h1>
        <p>Learn your favorite Syro Malabar Holy Mass songs with keyboard chords and step-by-step tutorials</p>
        
        <div class="search-bar">
            <input type="text" id="song-search" placeholder="Search songs by title...">
            <button type="button" onclick="searchSongs()">Search</button>
        </div>

        <div class="category-filters" id="category-filters">
            <button class="category-btn active" data-category="all">All Songs</button>
            {% for category in metadata.categories %}
            <button class="category-btn" data-category="{{ category.id }}">{{ category.icon }} {{ category.name }}</button>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

